core":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"田灣抵死架..d人又奶共..<br />\n個19區議員年年自動當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8152dd0a8811b0bbf3006db0a8448073b0364b8","tid":439541,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>田灣抵死架..d人又奶共..<br />\n個19區議員年年自動當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係無投佢都抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大撚把老弱婦孺唔撚出街比掌心雷去投 (老人院)<br />\n<br />\n好心佢間教會 (舊戲院) 就搬整做酒樓, 同嘉和街間護老院踢走做商場. (好撚耐之前係酒樓)"},{"pid":"dbc80cdb5ef1bfe362f9f961fac989606b19aef0","tid":439541,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日話香港落後但點解又係成車成車咁嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成車成車嘅豬入豬籠，你話豬籠先唔先進? 鳩噏!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5354389e31e031508707f1258b05c6b72622675f","tid":439541,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"因為佢隔離有間酒店好多大陸人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過搭車經後面條單行線，有架旅行車泊係到塞住條路司機又唔知係邊，塞左成粒鐘等個司機返開走架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d967a06b5cbc84b8b3827453d7cf6079d0f4987","tid":439541,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住樓上就仆街</blockquote><br />\n希望住樓上果啲唔好咁衝動扔野落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千奇唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫人犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999de6837cccab86703897b9ae1bddeb70bb71c","tid":439541,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"商埸間酒